narrations.value: Let's check out a data-driven widgets slide to share success metrics.
Since you have enabled personalized learning experiences, your team's adoption and product usage are improving over time.
Out of the top four features being used, Reporting is the one that benefits you the most.
Your Peer Health Rank is currently 77%, while customers similar to you in size are at 86%. To boost your rank, we suggest exploring benchmark-driven insights for high-touch segments.
Your users are most active on Wednesdays and Thursdays.
You have noteworthy weekend usage! It shows you're really making the most of our product. Keep it up!
And it seems, late afternoons are the prime time for user activity with our product!
No discernible patterns were detected for the day-of-the-month engagement. We will continue to monitor and provide meaningful recommendations as we learn more about your users.
Finally, you are on your way to becoming an expert! --awesome--
Just three more personalized learning sessions left!
In this Cast we will discuss your account usage and performance.
We will share best practices, along with new product recommendations.
And finally, we will also share how to reach the team.

and the majority of your expenses are for renting a home and a vehicle.
